# R3F & WebGL

- All canvas/Three usage stays behind **`"use client"`** components (e.g. under `src/components/background/`).
- Use **@react-three/fiber** (`useFrame`, canvas) and **@react-three/drei** as needed; import **three** types and math (`THREE`, `Vector3`, etc.) consistently with existing files.
- Keep animation and physics logic colocated (e.g. custom hooks in the same file) and avoid blocking the main thread with heavy work per frame; follow the patterns in `PolyhedronAnimation.tsx` / related modules.
